### labels

ggplot(data = ohi_data, aes(y = OHI_score, x = HDI, color=georegion_one)) + 
  geom_point() + 
    labs(y = "OHI score, 2017",
       x = "Human Development Index",
       title = "Countries with high human development have more sustainable oceans",
